"excerpt_area": {"text": "无论作为歌手还是演员都是香港女明星中的翘楚，据说其本人在香港异常受欢迎。那么。为何她在内地存在感不强，甚至还不如同时代的杨千嬅容祖儿陈慧琳梁咏琪等人呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63c9944d0526fe8235f5c58dc6cc53b4_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "122 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/35248031"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IseG91e6fo50HEAMaBzYzMDU4Mjkg/aeXrwUwADi1AUAGcggzNTI0ODAzMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1774856603.112742", "card_id": "Q_2021524697360150544", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 165}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 Epic 裁员把国区运营给裁了这件事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "E 宝真没了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-9132c62c597a4d9be9b636e20660d109.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021524697360150544"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIseG91e6fo50HEAMaCTExODk0MDc3MyD1iqLOBjAAOOwCQAdyEzIwMjE1MjQ2OTczNjAxNTA1NDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1774856603.113145", "card_id": "Q_2018997334248268237", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "把一个 300 斤的胖子物理压缩成魔鬼身材会发生什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "比如下方这样从头裹到脚的弹力紧身衣，假设自带均匀的无限收紧张力而且保持绝对密封永不破裂，物质和能量都无法逃逸。 现在给一个 178cm，300 斤的女胖穿上，衣服立刻均匀收紧，最终形成一个三围 90-60-90cm 完美超模身材的女体（体重通常 52-55kg） 则里面的人会发生什么？——由于是均匀收紧，不必担心内脏挤出的问题，因为根本没有挤出空间。 补充：如果继续无限收紧呢？里头会发生什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f8fa4755fdfd78dd1791adb53e46c795.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "117 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018997334248268237"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseG91e6fo50HEAMaCTExODg1MTY3MCCrp/3NBjAAOE1ACHITMjAxODk5NzMzNDI0ODI2ODIzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1774856603.113725", "card_id": "Q_2017979346778883711", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「广东今年没有回南天」引热议，今年广东回南天为何「缺席」？这是否意味着广东的回南天会越来越少？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "广东人狂喜！今年回南天，可能不来了！随着未来几天云量增加，早晚时分广州也不会那么清凉，夏天正在向我们走来。中午时分还穿着长袖外套的话，估计体感有些热了。珠海天气：今年没有回南天了 未来几天广州云量增多，早晚不再清凉，夏天悄悄靠近，中午穿长袖会明显偏热。评论区聊聊，留下你镜头里的广东的春天吧！详见：不用防潮不用擦墙！广东回南天可能要「缺席」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7322e8216da7bce7b8adc2e4f6bdaaac_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017979346778883711"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIseG91e6fo50HEAMaCTExODgxODAyNCCYv+7NBjAAOC5ACXITMjAxNzk3OTM0Njc3ODg4MzcxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1774856603.114446", "card_id": "Q_2021850492419008115", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 453}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "单依纯道歉称不知公司未获授权，停止《李白》后续所有演唱，李荣浩回应无需赔偿，怎样看待双方的处理方式？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[2 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-180d52eaf2b21d655dee72d4d6201d41_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021850492419008115"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIseG91e6fo50HEAMaCTExODk1MDczNiDh6abOBjAAOJYFQApyEzIwM